\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\n\t<!-- About Section -->\n\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 text-center\" style=\"margin-bottom:-60px;\">\n\t\t\t<h3>The Search for ExtraTerrestrial Intelligence <br/> At UC Berkeley </h3>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<section id=\"about\" class=\"container content-section text-justify\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8 col-md-offset-2\">\n\n\n\t\t\t\t<p> Berkeley SETI Research Center conducts experiments searching for electromagnetic signatures of intelligent extraterrestrial civilizations, spanning wavelengths from radio to visible light. We're the creators of the SETI@home volunteer computing software, that utilizes spare resources on volunteer computers to aid in processing data from radio telescopes. And we're excited to be participating in the new Breakthrough Listen initiative to use the Green Bank, Parkes, and Automated Planet Finder telescopes to dramatically expand the search for cosmic company. </p>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n\n\t<section class=\"container-fluid\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\n\t\t\t<a href=\"/participate\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-6 col-xs-12 btnnocaps btn-info\" style=\"height:170px;\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">SETI@home</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height:1.4;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJoin the search by harnessing your computer's spare processing power </p>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://seti.berkeley.edu/listen/\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-lg-4 col-md-6 btnnocaps btn-info\" style=\"height:170px;\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">Breakthrough Listen</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height:1.4;\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSponsors of the most comprehensive search ever for extraterrestrial civilizations </p>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n\n\n\t<section id=\"download\" class=\"content-section text-center \">\n\t\t<div class=\"download-section \">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"container \">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 \">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"news\">Social Media</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<!--<a href=\"http://startbootstrap.com/template-overviews/grayscale/ \" class=\"btn btn-default btn-lg \">Visit Download Page</a>-->\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n\n\t<!-- news section -->\n\n\t<section id=\"news\" class=\"content-section text-center \"> </section>\n\t<div class=\"news-section \">\n\t\t<div class=\"container \">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2\">\n\t\t\t\t<a aria-label=\"Twitter timeline\" class=\"twitter-timeline\" data-width=\"100%\" data-height=\"900\" data-theme=\"dark\" data-link-color=\"#259bdb\" href=\"https://twitter.com/BerkeleySETI\"></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\t<!-- Contact Section -->\n\n\t<!-- Footer -->\n\t<footer class=\"footer \">\n\t\t<div class=\"container text-center \">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row \">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-8 col-md-offset-4 col-sm-offset-2 \">\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"footer-social-block \">\n                                                <li><a aria-label=\"Facebook\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BerkeleySETI/\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\" aria-hidden=\"true\" title=\"Facebook\"></i></a></li>\n\n                                                <li><a aria-label=\"Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/BerkeleySETI\"><i class=\"fa fa-twitter\" aria-hidden=\"true\" title=\"Twitter\"></i></a></li>\n\n"
